long_desc.thetext:
Your package munge failed to build from source in current rawhide.
https://koji.fedoraproject.org/koji/taskinfo?taskID=17739620
For details on mass rebuild see https://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Fedora_26_Mass_Rebuild
This bug appears to have been reported against 'rawhide' during the Fedora 26 development cycle. Changing version to '26'.

munge-0.5.12 will build on Fedora 26 with the following changes to munge.spec:
1. Replace "BuildRequires: openssl-devel" with "BuildRequires: libgcrypt-devel"
2. Add "--with-crypto-lib=libgcrypt" to the %configure line
